{"tid":715491,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本要求中國在集裝箱放紅火蟻藥餌，中方表示為難","createTime":"2018-06-24T13:48:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-24T21:00:45.000Z","uid":53379,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1e8d23c3eb1cf451227155225f6eaa90fc4abe0c","tid":715491,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T13:48:30.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">日本要求中國在集裝箱放紅火蟻藥餌，中方表示為難</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n日本要求中國當局就輸往日本的集裝箱有紅火蟻問題採取措施，但中國表示有難度。<br />\n<br />\n日中韓三國環境部長會議23日在中國江蘇省蘇州市開幕。日本環境相中川雅治向中國生態環境部部長李幹傑提出，來自中國的集裝箱內多次發現原產南美的有毒紅火蟻，要求中方採取措施。<br />\n<br />\n日本環境省確認，去年6月以來12個都府縣共發現29次紅火蟻。單在6月，在大阪港卸貨的來自中國的集裝箱內，就發現了2000多隻紅火蟻的成蟲和蟲蛹。其後南韓也從中國進口的貨櫃中發現多達11個紅火蟻窩。<br />\n<br />\n中川雅治要求向中國方面在集裝箱放置含殺滅紅火蟻成分的誘餌，但中方表示為難，但李幹傑表示，將與相關部門合作，盡最大努力解決問題。<br />\n<br />\n另外，中國和日本又在會議上交換了備忘錄，內容包括中日在今後3年加快合作，改善細懸浮微粒PM2.5導致的空氣污染問題。<br />\n<br />\n中川雅治又南韓環境部部長金恩京舉行會談，談及日本海沿岸漂來標有韓文的塑料桶的問題，金恩京表示將會應對，防止問題再次發生。<br />\n<br />\n紅火蟻源自於南美洲巴拉那河流域，在攻擊人類時，會以腹部末端的螫針注入毒液，每隻紅火蟻可持續螫刺目標多次。被紅火蟻咬傷後，傷口會有強烈灼熱和痛癢感覺，傷口初期會出現白色膿包，然後變成半透明水泡，約十多天後水泡會逐漸乾涸脫落。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.thenewslens.com/article/98462\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.thenewslens.com%2Farticle%2F98462&d=r1m0JIOvSxi2dmEmn8NxCozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=b3f532eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.thenewslens.com/article/98462</a>"},{"pid":"1eacd1f643905ca2c02008e868af88cb6b5e4a79","tid":715491,"uid":76063,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T13:50:16.000Z","msg":"特登？"},{"pid":"e54dfa1e8c837247e983d7b7b6532937f0eeef80","tid":715491,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T13:51:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"769521a4eb33c7b43b85a40165fb874b7f66e55e","tid":715491,"uid":2404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T13:51:43.000Z","msg":"生化武器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcb0d6c3718bb32c981336c841b32aecb6f02bc7","tid":715491,"uid":76848,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T14:03:00.000Z","msg":"又贏 利害了我的"},{"pid":"8ed5fd263bddba14941cd19a5dd03a2aa3fffc14","tid":715491,"uid":50310,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T14:35:53.000Z","msg":"開滅蟲罰單，高原價三倍作刑罰<br />\n使乜勞氣"},{"pid":"4c7694b12681d62118393dcf555640718a123e54","tid":715491,"uid":91813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T16:20:20.000Z","msg":"點解唔禁入口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccfbfade1384889fbf1e1241a936676da8f8a3f0","tid":715491,"uid":50310,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4c7694b12681d62118393dcf555640718a123e54","tid":715491,"uid":91813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T16:20:20.000Z","msg":"點解唔禁入口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T20:47:05.000Z","msg":"倒返轉，你估到邊隻貨櫃出事咩？<br />\n不過，要人額外做嘢搞衛生<br />\n罰款天經地意<br />\n比侵侵罰關稅更有意思<br />\n你若先搞衛生，邊度得閒罰你？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"512848b49c623a5b7ccf7574a74460b6943fa07b","tid":715491,"uid":24044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T20:48:40.000Z","msg":"要不是..."},{"pid":"aa908ae78c4f05383573edb2e9b4dc4913d77590","tid":715491,"uid":175539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T20:52:00.000Z","msg":"專登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3177a32cc0e8f90c5d2eab830b151a87653f0003","tid":715491,"uid":37586,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ccfbfade1384889fbf1e1241a936676da8f8a3f0","tid":715491,"uid":50310,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4c7694b12681d62118393dcf555640718a123e54","tid":715491,"uid":91813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited